[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      382[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         // The retraining pipeline recomputes features with recent data,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      383[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         // trains a new model version, validates on a held-out set, and
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      384[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         // promotes only if the new model outperforms the current one.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      385[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      386[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     // Log the evaluation for audit purposes.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      387[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     write evaluation summary to S3:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      388[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         s3://churn-scoring-results/monitoring/date={evaluation_date}/eval.json
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      389[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      390[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     RETURN { auc_pr, ece, retrain_triggered: (auc_pr < 0.40 OR ece > 0.10) }
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      391[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      392[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
